{"tid":1354287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請幫手推呢個前線,後方和理非 理應有既共識post","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:40:31.000Z","uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d7697423d2a3c4a065b6dfd254664f2bf29cd1","tid":1354287,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"有見前線對後方/和理非 散水/be water 不滿<br />\n和理非又對前線有時死守不退不滿<br />\n所以想出個post 理順情況<br />\n定下某d 條件先可以嗌走 / 某d 情況可以守&amp;戰<br />\n<br />\n1. 午12點前如未有包圍網形成，不需撤退<br />\n警犬既機動優勢係午夜後先明顯拉開<br />\n12點後可以快速形成包圍網<br />\n如後方仍有大理和理非在場睇水，set 路障，不需過早退<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察full gear 裝備隊不夠500人 以上，戰線不夠兩條，不需撤退<br />\n觀乎上環一戰，二三百人既防暴隊，一條戰線，勇武派係可以應付有餘<br />\n<br />\n3. 後方和理非人數下降至勇武派5倍以下/ 3千人以下，前方必需要撤退<br />\n<br />\n4. 日落前任何勇武行動，如現場有一萬示威者以上，均可放膽進攻<br />\n<br />\n5. 午夜12點後，今日23/7/2019 ，抗爭覺醒仍未足夠，避免一千人以上被一網打盡，必須安全全數退場，撤退另一日再勇武過"},{"pid":"a3790f75c6dc79c9fc6cd6d6e307bbbb0b9c36e4","tid":1354287,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"727 反警黑"},{"pid":"b7bff9c492a5d315837dfd1f3e07007415551b7d","tid":1354287,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:13:01.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 小弟嘅白宮聯署差15%咋<br />\n希望request國際人道救援/援助 人道監察<br />\n已經有八萬四千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=109507bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition